metadata.name: The Strange #1
metadata.description: "I long for the days when life was simpler, when the sun shone bright and the air was fresh. But those days are gone, and I am left with this dystopian reality. I can only hope that someday, somehow, we will find a way to break free from the chains that bind us and create a better world for ourselves and those who come after us. But for now, I must keep my head down, do as I'm told, and survive."
